  <section>
    <h1>Index Group Overview</h1>
    <p>Index Group serves as the holding platform for a suite of national indexes designed to establish unified standards in corporate excellence.</p>
    <p>It exists to address the fragmentation in recognition systems, providing a structured, enduring framework that prioritizes governance over episodic awards.</p>
    <p>Our long-term vision adopts a decade-scale, archival mindset, ensuring continuity and relevance for institutions in Botswana and beyond.</p>
    <p>Governance is at the core of our positioning, with methodologies developed in alignment with international best practices while rooted in local contexts.</p>
    <p>Developed with international collaborators like Temporal AI (U.S.A.).</p>
